Actions.Text: REFERRED TO TOURISM, PARKS, ARTS AND SPORTS DEVELOPMENT

Title: Relates to notice by museums of art stolen during the Nazi era in Europe
Summary: Requires museums to post a notice with the display of any art stolen during the Nazi era in Europe.
ActClause: AN ACT to amend the education law, in relation to notice of art stolen during the Nazi era in Europe
